 █ ▀ █ █ █▀▄ █ █  █ 
 ▀   ▀ ▀ ▀ ▀ ▀ ▀▀▀▀

Commands:
  miko completion          generate shell completion script
  miko acp                 start ACP (Agent Client Protocol) server
  miko mcp                 manage MCP (Model Context Protocol) servers
  miko [project]           start miko tui                                                  [default]
  miko attach <url>        attach to a running miko server
  miko run [message..]     run miko with a message
  miko debug               debugging and troubleshooting tools
  miko providers           manage AI providers and credentials                       [aliases: auth]
  miko agent               manage agents
  miko upgrade [target]    upgrade miko to the latest or a specific version
  miko uninstall           uninstall miko and remove all related files
  miko serve               starts a headless miko server
  miko models [provider]   list all available models
  miko export [sessionID]  export session data as JSON
  miko import <file>       import session data from JSON file or URL
  miko github              manage GitHub agent
  miko pr <number>         fetch and checkout a GitHub PR branch, then run miko
  miko session             manage sessions
  miko plugin <module>     install plugin and update config                          [aliases: plug]
  miko db                  database tools

Positionals:
  project  path to start miko in                                                            [string]

Options:
  -h, --help         show help                                                             [boolean]
  -v, --version      show version number                                                   [boolean]
      --print-logs   print logs to stderr                                                  [boolean]
      --log-level    log level                  [string] [choices: "DEBUG", "INFO", "WARN", "ERROR"]
      --pure         run without external plugins                                          [boolean]
      --port         port to listen on                                         [number] [default: 0]
      --hostname     hostname to listen on                           [string] [default: "127.0.0.1"]
      --mdns         enable mDNS service discovery (defaults hostname to 0.0.0.0)
                                                                          [boolean] [default: false]
      --mdns-domain  custom domain name for mDNS service (default: miko.local)
                                                                    [string] [default: "miko.local"]
      --cors         additional domains to allow for CORS                      [array] [default: []]
  -m, --model        model to use in the format of provider/model                           [string]
  -c, --continue     continue the last session                                             [boolean]
  -s, --session      session id to continue                                                 [string]
      --fork         fork the session when continuing (use with --continue or --session)   [boolean]
      --prompt       prompt to use                                                          [string]
      --agent        agent to use                                                           [string]
"
`;

